{
  "stem": "20711.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] came to live with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the father with his friends also spent the weekend in our house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because we had the car, we were picking them up and big-- bring them back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I never forget an incident as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day my parents threw a pretty big party for the Polish refugees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were about 30 of them in our house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were heavy drinking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Polish people do like vodka and-- they were-- everybody, including my father, who is not a drinker, I remember they were all drinking and talking and very much politics.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somehow the subject of the anti-Semitism came up, and it turned out this people were very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were aristocratic and intellectuals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] father was a mayor of a city next to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some of them were lawyers and artist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One was an architect, I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I even remember some of them by their name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they started to talk against the Jews, and my father is a very patient and very tolerant man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it took a long time before he decided that was it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said it very quietly in German, which most of them did understood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Gentleman's, I think you must know you are in a Jewish man's home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were all shocked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had a tradition not to display any religious artifact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anybody who walked into our house, they didn't know if it's Catholic or Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We didn't had anything in our house to give away any influence of any religious background.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I assumed they were surprised to get so much generosity from a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
